\begin_layout Standard

\shape italic
In the discussion below, let 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 be a random variable that follows Beta distribution with parameter 
\begin_inset Formula $a,b\in\mathbb{R}^{+}.$
\end_inset


