= & \int\exp\left\{ \left(x-\mu+\frac{1}{2}\lambda_{3}^{-1}\lambda_{2}\right)^{T}\lambda_{3}\left(x-\mu+\frac{1}{2}\lambda_{3}^{-1}\lambda_{2}\right)-\frac{1}{4}\lambda_{2}\lambda_{3}^{-1}\lambda_{2}+\lambda_{2}^{T}\mu+\lambda_{1}-1\right\} dx\\
