\begin_layout Lemma
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\{X_{i}\}_{i=1}^{m}$
\end_inset

 be a collection of independent random variables such that 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{i}\in\mathbb{R}^{n_{i}}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{i}\sim\mathrm{MVN}(\mu_{i},\Sigma_{i}).$
\end_inset

