 QUOTE independence), 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{i}:=\sum_{j=1}^{n_{i}}t_{ij}X_{ij}\perp Y_{i'}=\sum_{j=1}^{n_{i'}}t_{i'j}X_{i'j}$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $i\neq i'.$
\end_inset

