\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "lem: sum of independent MVN"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 it follows that 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle t,X\right\rangle =\sum_{i=1}^{m}(\sum_{j=1}^{n_{i}}t_{ij}X_{ij})$
