We fix 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\Vert \cdot\right\Vert $
\end_inset

 to be any consistent matrix norm.
 First, we note that for 
\begin_inset Formula $H\in\mathrm{GL}_{\mathbb{R}}(n)$
\end_inset

