The following distribution 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p(x\vert\sigma^{2},q)=\frac{q}{2(2\sigma^{2})^{1/q}\Gamma(1/q)}\exp\left(-\frac{\left|x\right|^{q}}{2\sigma^{2}}\right)\tag{1}
\]

