 & \ \ -x\log x-x-\frac{1}{2}\bigg(\log2\pi+\log\frac{1}{\alpha}\bigg)-\frac{1}{12x}-O\bigg(\frac{1}{x^{3}}\bigg)-\alpha\log x\\
