\end{align*}

\end_inset

Note that 
\begin_inset Formula $\log(1+\frac{\alpha}{x})=\frac{\alpha}{x}+O(\frac{1}{x^{2}})=\frac{\alpha}{x}-\frac{\alpha^{2}}{2x^{2}}+O(\frac{1}{x^{3}})$
