 & =\exp\biggp{m\biggp{1-\frac{1}{2}m^{-1}\xi^{2}+O(m^{-2})}}\\
 & \propto\exp\biggp{-\frac{\xi^{2}}{2}}=\exp\biggp{-\frac{m(\theta-\theta_{0})^{2}}{2}},
